text: Joining Yio Chu Kang Tennis Academy has been great for me. The coaches are professional and approachable, offering personalised guidance that has improved my skills. The tennis courts are clean, and the training programs are well-organised, accommodating all levels of play. What I love most is the welcoming atmosphere and the highly accessible venue, just next to Yio Chu Kang MRT.

Good place to pick up tennis as a beginner. The group class was a great way to start as all of us started with a similar skill level, definitely less intimidating as we were able to encourage one another. Great experience for a start üëçüèª
